# 1. https://discord.com/developers/applications → New Application → Bot → Reset Token
# 2. Enable Privileged Gateway Intents: SERVER MEMBERS + PRESENCE
# 3. Invite bot to your DeLuca server (OAuth2 URL Generator: bot scope, permissions: Read Members / View Channels)
# 4. Discord: Developer Mode ON → right-click your server → Copy Server ID

DISCORD_BOT_TOKEN=paste_bot_token_here
DISCORD_GUILD_ID=paste_your_server_id_here
PORT=8787
